<section class="services">
  <h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Our Services</h2>
  <!-- List of gym services -->
  <div class="service-list">
    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Private Classes</h3>
      <p>Our private classes offer personalized training tailored to your specific fitness goals. Our certified trainers work closely with you to design a customized workout plan, ensuring safe and effective progress. Perfect for beginners or those looking to reach new performance levels.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Group Classes</h3>
      <p>Our group classes are designed to inspire and motivate. Whether it is yoga, spinning, or HIIT, you will find a vibrant community of members sharing the same goal: staying active and healthy. Have fun while reaching your fitness goals with the guidance of our experienced instructors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>State-of-the-Art Equipment</h3>
      <p>Our state-of-the-art equipment is designed to meet the needs of all fitness levels, from beginners to advanced athletes. Explore our modern treadmills, strength machines, and functional training tools that make every workout effective and enjoyable.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

